<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Endemic to Amazonian Brazil, apparently very rare although several, apparently unsupported records from different states are included in Flora do Brasil 2020 under construction.</paragraph>
